{"kind":"article","primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"level":2,"text":"RFID 标签数据结构","type":"heading","anchor":"RFID-%E6%A0%87%E7%AD%BE%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"本库的功能都是围绕 RFID 标签而设计开发，了解一些 RFID 标签的基本信息，可以更好的去理解 RFID 相关功能","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"RFID 标签的的基本数据区域大致如下如所示："}]},{"type":"orderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"RESERVED 包含 kill 和 access 两个密码数据，长度都为 32 bit，默认密码都是 00000000"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"EPC 包含三个部分："}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"crc : 循环冗余校验"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"pc : epc 标签长度控制字"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"epc : 具体的 epc 用户数据","type":"text"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"盘点时读取到 epc 数据长度取决于 pc 的高 5 位值，epc长度转为为pc值示例："},{"type":"text","text":"\n"},{"type":"text","text":"epc 长度为 6 个字 (96 bit)： 6 字 = 0011 0000 0000 0000 = 0x3000"},{"type":"text","text":"\n"},{"type":"text","text":"epc 长度为 9 个字 (144 bit)： 9 字 = 0100 1000 0000 0000 = 0x4800"},{"type":"text","text":"\n"},{"type":"text","text":"epc 长度为 15 个字 (240 bit)： 15 字 = 0111 1000 0000 0000 = 0x7800"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"TID 区域均为 tid 数据。一般来说，tid 长度为 96 bit, 是唯一且无法修改的"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"USER 区域均为 user 数据，其长度取决于具体标签，不同类型标签的 USER 区域容量可能不同","type":"text"}]}]}]}],"kind":"content"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"这篇文章主要介绍一些 RFID 相关的基本知识，方便你能更好的了解 RFIDManager 库"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.rfid.RFIDManager\/documentation\/RFIDManager\/RFID-----","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.rfid.RFIDManager\/docu